external_knowledge:
- "Treasure chest" refers to the inventory of products;
- "Jewels in the treasure chest" metaphorically represents the products;
- "Shone the brightest" refers to the products that have generated the highest total revenue;
- "Value (price)" refers to the price of the products;
- "Gold mined" is a metaphor for total revenue from sales;
- "Type (category 1)" refers to the product category being 1, such as Carpet Cleaners.

sql:
SELECT SUM(total_amount) AS total_revenue
FROM orders
WHERE status = 'delivered';
